parameters.name: Julian Date
parameters.description:
Time of the spacecraft position shown in the record, expressed as         
                          a Julian date.

parameters.name: Radius
parameters.description:
Spacecraft Radius:  Distance of the spacecraft from the center of         
                          the Moon.

parameters.name: Velocity
parameters.description: Spacecraft Velocity:  Absolute velocity of the spacecraft.

parameters.name: Latitude
parameters.description:
Sub-spacecraft Latitude:  The selenographic latitude of the point         
                          directly beneath the spacecraft, with north latitude as positive.

parameters.name: Longitude
parameters.description:
Sub-spacecraft Longitude:  The selenographic longitude of the point       
                          directly beneath the spacecraft, with east longitude as positive.

parameters.name: Altitude
parameters.description:
Spacecraft Altitude:  The distance of the spacecraft above the            
                          surface of the moon, assuming that the moon is a sphere of                
                          radius 1738 km.

parameters.name: SG X
parameters.description:
Spacecraft X-coordinate in the SG coordinate system, in units of          
                          kilometers.

parameters.name: SG Y
parameters.description:
Spacecraft Y-coordinate in the SG coordinate system, in units of          
                          kilometers.

parameters.name: SG Z
parameters.description:
Spacecraft Z-coordinate in the SG coordinate system, in units of          
                          kilometers.

parameters.name: SSE X
parameters.description:
Spacecraft X-coordinate in the SSE coordinate system, in units of          
                          kilometers.

parameters.name: SSE Y
parameters.description:
Spacecraft Y-coordinate in the SSE coordinate system, in units of          
                          kilometers.

parameters.name: SSE Z
parameters.description:
Spacecraft Z-coordinate in the SSE coordinate system, in units of          
                          kilometers.

parameters.name: GSE X
parameters.description:
Spacecraft X-coordinate in the GSE coordinate system, in units of         
                          Earth radii.

parameters.name: GSE Y
parameters.description:
Spacecraft Y-coordinate in the GSE coordinate system, in units of         
                          Earth radii.

parameters.name: GSE Z
parameters.description:
Spacecraft Z-coordinate in the GSE coordinate system, in units of         
                          Earth radii.

parameters.name: GSM Y
parameters.description:
Spacecraft Y-coordinate in the GSM coordinate system, in units of         
                          Earth radii.

parameters.name: GSM Z
parameters.description:
Spacecraft Z-coordinate in the GSM coordinate system, in units of         
                          Earth radii.
